  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00778', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於我國托育服務與相關政策，下列敘述何者正確？', '["「照顧」是托育服務的首要工作，「教育」則是托育服務的附帶功能", "托育服務是一種替代父母照顧的兒童照顧方案", "居家式托育服務提供者若是住在隔壁的鄰居，不需要額外範定其法定資格", "在我國的幼托整合政策中，將「幼兒園」依收托年齡分為「幼稚園」及「托兒所」"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2fbac3fb0314", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ec43feddf564", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 48, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00779', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於家庭社會工作的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["在方法上，是以家庭為整體實施的社會工作", "在對象上，以服務家庭中有問題的成員為主", "在評估上，包含整個家庭及其成員", "在內容上，提供各項家庭服務"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2fbac3fb0314", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ec43feddf564", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 49, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00780', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '就生態觀點（ecologicalperspective）分析，小明的母親常年凌晨4點到9點在早餐店工作，其母親工作的 時間、型態等對小明而言是屬於下列何者？', '["微視系統（micro-system）", "中介系統（meso-system）", "外在系統（exo-system）", "鉅視系統（macro-system）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2fbac3fb0314", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ec43feddf564", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 50, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00781', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-b3f42868', 'sub-elementary-64311456-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '我國憲法第23條規定：「以上各條列舉之自由權利，除為防止妨害他人自由、避免緊急危難、維持社會', '["比例原則", "法律保留原則", "誠實信用原則", "信賴保護原則"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "57e6993d4375", "answer_pdf_sha1": "215bbf5687be", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公民與英文", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00782', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-b3f42868', 'sub-elementary-64311456-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '1989 年國小老師李幸長發起「無殼蝸牛運動」，夜宿臺北市忠孝東路，抗議政府漠視人民的居住權益。 後來，無住屋運動轉型為「崔媽媽基金會」，透過協助弱勢族群解決租屋問題，落實「居者適其屋」的 理念。關於「無殼蝸牛運動」發展到「崔媽媽基金會」之成立，下列敘述何者正確？', '["由非營利組織轉型為營利組織", "原強調利他主義後轉為主張利己導向", "原以公益為使命後轉為重視成本效益", "從倡議的社會運動轉為成立服務性的社團"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "57e6993d4375", "answer_pdf_sha1": "215bbf5687be", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公民與英文", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00783', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-b3f42868', 'sub-elementary-64311456-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '近年來雙薪家庭比例上升，由於父母忙於工作，因此托兒所、安親班等機構成為安置孩童的重要處所。 根據統計，臺灣目前有政府立案的各種安親班、補習班、才藝班數量遠遠超過全臺超商數量。此現象說 明隨著社會變遷，家庭的何種功能正在轉變？', '["生育功能", "經濟功能", "社會化功能", "傳遞社會地位"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "57e6993d4375", "answer_pdf_sha1": "215bbf5687be", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公民與英文", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00784', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-b3f42868', 'sub-elementary-64311456-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '所謂「友善職場」，就是無歧視、重平等的職場。在職場中，勞工與雇主彼此尊重、合作，共同打造一 個性別平權的工作環境。下列何種作法，最有助於促進「友善職場」？', '["開放同志勞工因伴侶生病時可請家庭照顧假", "營造玻璃天花板環境以便落實性別實質平等", "健全性別職業隔離制度以保障女性就業機會", "降低女性勞動參與率以避免蠟燭兩頭燒現象"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "57e6993d4375", "answer_pdf_sha1": "215bbf5687be", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公民與英文", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
